{"type":"message","id":"2af82422","parentId":"3c6344b5","timestamp":"2026-03-02T06:25:30.009Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-03-02 07:09 GMT+1] You are managing Z.E Digital Tech (@zedigitaltech) on X/Twitter.\n\n**Task:** Create 25 engaging posts to build community and engagement.\n\n**Browser setup:** Use the `openclaw` browser profile (already logged in to @zedigitaltech).\n\n**Post pattern:**\n1. Navigate to: `https://x.com/compose/post`\n2. Type the post (max 280 chars!)\n3. Click \"Post\" button\n\n**Content themes:**\n\nCommunity Building:\n- \"Who else is building in hospitality tech? Drop your handle 👇\"\n- \"Shoutout to all the hotel operators embracing technology!\"\n- \"The future of hospitality is being built right now. Who's building it?\"\n\nThread Starters:\n- \"Unpopular opinion thread: Why most hotel tech fails 🧵\"\n- \"5 things I wish every hotel knew about AI: 🧵\"\n- \"The biggest myths about voice AI in hospitality 🧵\"\n\nEngagement Bait:\n- \"Reply with your worst hotel tech experience. Go.\"\n- \"What's ONE feature you wish hotels had?\"\n- \"If you could ask a hotel AI anything, what would it be?\"\n\nBrand Value:\n- Z.E Digital Tech mission\n- Why voice AI matters\n- Customer-first approach\n\n**IMPORTANT:**\n- Keep ALL posts under 280 characters\n- Track how many you successfully posted\n- Report final count when done"}],"timestamp":1772432730008}}
